reviews.review_text: Apart from view there is nothing which i can say good or excellent had to wait for each dish nearly 40 min on Christmas day dinner if you think restaurant was packed hence there was a huge delay then wait for the surprise it's was not even 20% full, I was promised prawn masala when asked the size of the prawn I was told it will be medium size  but got ultra small which we just left intact. Horrible service and no value for money.

Ambience and service was good. Food quantity as per pricing is also reasonable but I felt the food taste was average. Can't say that I really enjoyed the food. Tummy was full but not satisfied. I tried only few items so they might be having some other items worth trying. Can check out this place once...
